( Causes respiratory tract irritation. Breathing )Tj
-5.1907 -1.20232 Td
(vapors may cause drowsiness and dizziness. Causes eye irritation. Aspira\tion hazard if )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(swallowed. Can enter lungs and cause damage. Prolonged or repeated conta\ct causes )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(defatting of the skin with irritation, dryness, and cracking. This mater\ial has been )Tj
0 -1.20001 TD
(reported to be susceptible to autoxidation and therefore should be class\ified as )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(peroxidizable. May cause central nervous system depression. May form exp\losive )Tj
0 -1.2 TD
(peroxides. Hygroscopic \(absorbs moisture from the air\). )Tj
/TT1 1 Tf
T*
(Target Organs: )Tj
/TT0 1 Tf
(Central nervous system, respiratory system, eyes, skin. )Tj
